'''先知以利亚会堂'''（Eliyahu Hanavi Synagogue；كنيس النبي إلياهو；בית הכנסת אל）是[[埃及|埃及]][[亚历山大港|亚历山大港]]的一个[[犹太会堂|犹太会堂]]。它建于1354年，在1798年法国入侵埃及期间被法国炸毁，1850年在[[穆罕默德·阿里王朝|穆罕默德·阿里王朝]]统治下重建<ref>{{Cite book |last1=Hosni |first1=Yousrya Abdel-Aziz |title=Alexandria: Historical and Archaeological Guide |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ZhXucP_3Z_oC&pg=PA75 |year=2010 |publisher=American University in Cairo Press |isbn=978-977-479-185-7 |pages=95–96}}</ref>。1956年大批犹太人离开埃及后，留在亚历山大港的犹太人非常之少，但是该会堂仍在举行仪式<ref>{{Cite journal |last=Gazzar |first=Brenda |date=23 October 2008 |title=Alexandria's last Jews sad to see empty shul on Simhat Torah |journal=[[The_Jerusalem_Post|The Jerusalem Post]] |accessdate=2011-02-17 |url=http://www.jpost.com/Home/Article.aspx?id=118029}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.haaretz.com/jewish-world/jewish-world-news/replica-of-ancient-egypt-synagogue-arrives-at-tel-aviv-museum-1.439895 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-12-24 |archive-date=2015-09-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150924162952/http://www.haaretz.com/jewish-world/jewish-world-news/replica-of-ancient-egypt-synagogue-arrives-at-tel-aviv-museum-1.439895 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。该会堂自2012年起由于安全原因关闭。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/1/64/51913/Egypt/Politics-/Jewish-festivals-cancelled-at-Alexandria-synagogue.aspx |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-12-24 |archive-date=2017-02-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170213081210/http://english.ahram.org.eg/NewsContent/1/64/51913/Egypt/Politics-/Jewish-festivals-cancelled-at-Alexandria-synagogue.aspx |dead-url=no }}</ref>

